If you see the JDK source code for HashSet hashcode:

    public int hashCode() {
        int h = 0;
        Iterator&lt;E&gt; i = iterator();
        while (i.hasNext()) {
            E obj = i.next();
            if (obj != null)
                h += obj.hashCode();
        }
        return h;
    }

The set is being iterated for calculating each member hashcode.

